Tip the Artist

Artist Bio

Herrera has written his way into his fan’s hearts over the course of his 21-year long career, selling more than 1.5 million records and touring the world. With an endless archive of tracks to choose from, Herrera will be performing a highly anticipated set list full of MXPX and TUMBLEDOWN favorites. With the set lists varying from city to city, (or in this case, Web show) fans are encouraged to request their favorite tracks for a possible impromptu addition. Space is limited during these shorter Stage It shows. So get your picks in early!
